TXml 1.0.0 API

Packages 
Package Description
txml
Contains API of TXml library.
txml.database
Contains database statements.
txml.database.model
Contains data model for package txml.database.
txml.interpreter
Contains interpreter for instructions (commands) in package txml.interpreter.command.
txml.interpreter.command
Contains commands class, commands implement instructions from package txml.parser.
txml.interpreter.command.model
Contains data model for package txml.interpreter.command.
txml.interpreter.model
Contains data model for package txml.interpreter.
txml.load
Contains classes for reading new XML document.
txml.load.model
Contains data model for package txml.load.
txml.parser
Contains antlr classes (http://www.antlr.org/).
txml.snapshot
Contains classes for snapshot (XML document valid in specified time instant).
txml.snapshot.model
Contains data model for package txml.snapshot.
txml.xpath.model
Contains classes for XPath queries.
txml.xpath.sort
Contains classes for sorting XPath result.
txml.xpath.sort.model
Contains data model for package txml.xpath.sort.
